      include subpanels for detached buildings, dedicated circuits for shop equipment, EV charging for commuters, and
      panel upgrades on older homes that have grown into modern electrical loads.
    </p>
    <p>
      Detached buildings and outbuildings are particularly common in Hudsonville. The right approach there usually
